250.5	Bernard_Madoff	Bernard Madoff	Bernard Lawrence "Bernie" Madoff (born April 29, 1938) is a former American businessman, stockbroker, investment advisor, and financier. He is the former non-executive chairman of the NASDAQ stock market, and the admitted operator of a Ponzi scheme that is considered to be the largest financial fraud in U.S. history.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a4/BernardMadoff.jpg/220px-BernardMadoff.jpg
